{
  "id": "adv_event_2311_01_01",
  "title": "目指すは\n100連勝",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――NEXT VENUSグランプリ準決勝の直後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Right after the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix semifinals",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.4200000643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "（NEXT VENUSグランプリの準決勝で）\n（私達はサニーピースに負けた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(In the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix semifinals‚)\n(we lost to Sunny Peace.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2333335597,
      "endTime": 8.024059077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "（ステージで私達は全力を出し切った。だから負けても）\n（後悔はなかった。……後悔はなかったけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We gave it our all on stage. So even if we lost‚)\n(we had no regrets… I\\we had no regrets‚ but)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2107259154,
      "endTime": 18.090090692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……っ……はあ……でも、やっぱり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ugh… Haa… But still…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.276757435,
      "endTime": 23.9767575304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.276757435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "…………悔しいなあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…… I’m so frustrated…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1900908828,
      "endTime": 26.4825846315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.2122436818
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6759180029
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん……せやな\n悔しいんは……悔しいな、ほんま……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan… You’re right.\nIt’s frustrating… It is frustrating‚ really…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6759180029,
      "endTime": 35.4759180029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.6625846982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "うちら、めっちゃ頑張ったもん\n毎日毎日自主練だってして……が、頑張った……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We worked so hard.\nWe practiced every single day… We‚ we worked hard… Ugh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.6625846982,
      "endTime": 44.6932193875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.8798862259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと～\nなんで二人が先に泣いちゃうの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hey~\nWhy are you two crying first…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.8798862259,
      "endTime": 50.3341263573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "私だって……悔しくて……ほ、本当は……\nが、我慢して……っ、次も、頑張ろうって……ぐすっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m… frustrated too… I-in fact…\nI-I was holding it in… and trying to… say that we’ll do our best next time… Sob.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5407928904,
      "endTime": 63.1168243846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.5407928904
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.330157737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うう……うわああああああ……っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uuu… Waaaaaaaah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.330157737,
      "endTime": 70.96666666670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "（悔しくて、三人で泣いて）\n（もっと強くなろうと誓い合った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Frustrated‚ the three of us cried)\n(and vowed to become stronger.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4106989663,
      "endTime": 77.05425918499999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.4353470356
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "（二度と負けないように……）\n（まだ見ぬ高みへ、自らの翼で羽ばたくために……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(So that we would never lose again…)\n(To soar to new heights with our own wings…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2609259089,
      "endTime": 84.1439871271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "（あの時流した悔し涙を、私は絶対に忘れない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I’ll never forget the tears of frustration I shed that day.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3573202889,
      "endTime": 89.1222636979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……ここは……？\n確か、ダンスの練習中に意識が遠くなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… Where… am I?\nI’m sure I lost consciousness while practicing dance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.4422632655,
      "endTime": 101.0762752971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "私ったら体力が尽きて、また練習中に眠っちゃったのね\nじゃあ、さっきのは夢……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I must have run out of stamina and fallen asleep during practice again.\nSo‚ what I just saw was a dream…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2696084779,
      "endTime": 109.6268651764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、瑠依ちゃん！　目が覚めたんだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Rui-chan! You’re awake!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8401983381,
      "endTime": 114.17285606819999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 166.66491440000186
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 899.3243968000115
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "気分どうなん？　具合悪いんやったら\n{user}さん呼んで来ようか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How are you feeling? If you’re not feeling well‚\nshould I call {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3899277171,
      "endTime": 120.13514294219999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんならきっと\n瑠依ちゃんを寮までおんぶして連れて行ってくれるで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure {user}-san\nwill carry you back to the dorm on his back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3484763901,
      "endTime": 126.1838276666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "おんぶ……\nだ、大丈夫よ！　ちゃんと自分の足で歩けるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Carry me on his back…?\nN-no‚ I’m fine! I can walk on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3704945048,
      "endTime": 131.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、元気そうで安心したわ\n……ん？　瑠依ちゃん、険しい顔してどないしたん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I’m relieved to see you’re okay.\n…Hmm? Rui-chan‚ why do you have such a serious look on your face?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7904879213,
      "endTime": 141.4141611697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ、優、すみれ\n私達、強くなったわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ Yu‚ Sumire.\nWe’ve gotten stronger‚ haven’t we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.600828008,
      "endTime": 147.1259752553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前やん。グランプリの頃より\n歌もダンスもかなり上達して、安定感も増したわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. We’ve improved a lot in both singing and dancing\nsince the Grand Prix‚ and we’ve gotten more stable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.3126419982,
      "endTime": 155.2181593856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロに移籍してからは仕事の幅も広がって\n応援してくれる人の数も増えたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we joined Hoshimi Prods‚ the scope of our work has broadened‚\nand the number of people who support us has increased.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.4314925473,
      "endTime": 162.76140168130001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "サニピに負けてから、うちらは必死に頑張った\nその結果がライブバトル破竹の98連勝……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After losing to Sunny Peace‚ we worked really hard.\nAnd the result is an unbroken 98 wins in live battles…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.9480685195,
      "endTime": 171.46571034989998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "今も連勝記録を更新中で\n100連勝の大台も目前やもんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re still on a winning streak‚\nand we’re on the verge of 100th straight win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.6590434353,
      "endTime": 177.44317048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2311_01_01-rui013.m4a",
